videos.description: UNC's Coby White makes some slick moves in between defenders, then drives to the rim for an easy lay-in.
videos.headline: White weaves through defenders for score

videos.description: Chris Lykes drains a 3 from both ends of the arc on back-to-back possessions to give Miami the lead over North Carolina.
videos.headline: Lykes hits back-to-back 3-pointers to put Miami in front

videos.description: Nassir Little takes a pass from Coby White in the paint and slams it home to put UNC up 49-46 over Miami.
videos.headline: Little goes airborne for the two-handed jam
